OL,3,CSwansea's big fly-tipping problem
OL,4,Cthat's getting worse
OL,6,FFly-tipping in Swansea has risen by 22
OL,7,Fper cent in just 12 months, according
OL,8,Fto new figures.
OL,10,FSwansea Council says it received 2,316
OL,11,Freports of fly-tipping in 2023/24 - up
OL,12,Ffrom the previous year's number of
OL,13,F1,898.
OL,15,FSwansea Council says the figures are
OL,16,Fdisappointing and it is doing all it
OL,17,Fcan to tackle the problem.
