OL,3,CSwansea's big fly-tipping problem
OL,4,Cthat's getting worse
OL,6,FCouncillor Peter Black says he
OL,7,Frequested the data after noticing an
OL,8,Fincrease in rubbish and waste dumped
OL,9,Fon roadsides and on private land in
OL,10,Fhis ward of Cwmbrwla.
OL,12,FMr Black is concerned with the impact
OL,13,Ffly-tipping is having on local
OL,14,Fresidents and businesses.
OL,16,F"It's quite disturbing," Cllr Black
OL,17,Ftold ITV Cymru Wales.
