OL,3,CSwansea's big fly-tipping problem
OL,4,Cthat's getting worse
OL,6,F"Since I started getting these
OL,7,Ffigures, it's shown quite a big jump
OL,8,Fin the number of incidents (of fly-
OL,9,Ftipping) in the city.
OL,11,F"This is a very anti-social activity,
OL,12,Fit has an impact on the community and
OL,13,Ftheir perception of their environment
OL,14,Fand we do need to start clamping down
OL,15,Fon this."
OL,17,FSwansea resident Helen Thomas says the
OL,18,Fsight of dumped rubbish on the streets
OL,19,F"is not a good look".
